Sentencas: Planar solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) are one of energy conversion systems with high efficiency and low environmental damage.
Titulo: The effect of cell shape on the warpage in solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: During the fabrication of the cells, the mismatch between the thermo-elastic material properties of the components causes the warpage of cells.
Titulo: The effect of cell shape on the warpage in solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The warpage can reduce the performance of the cells.
Titulo: The effect of cell shape on the warpage in solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In this study, the planar anode supported half cells are made by tape casting and co-sintering and the effect of the cell shape on the warpage of cells has been investigated under identical conditions.
Titulo: The effect of cell shape on the warpage in solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Half cells with three common shapes (circle, square and rectangle) are made and the warpage of all samples is analyzed.
Titulo: The effect of cell shape on the warpage in solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The results demonstrate that under these fabrication conditions, rectangular cells are flatter than the square cells and square cells are flatter than the circular cells.
Titulo: The effect of cell shape on the warpage in solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: All specimens, in spite of the difference in shape, show a semi-cylindrical curvature.
Titulo: The effect of cell shape on the warpage in solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: This work also provides more accurate criteria for the comparison of cell warpage.
Titulo: The effect of cell shape on the warpage in solid oxide fuel cells
